                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230409-185-off985 t18230409-185-cd986"></join>, a jacket, value 8 s.; a waistcoat, value 3 s.; a pair of trowsers, value 2 s.; two pair of stockings, value 1 s., and a hat, value 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
